{"id":232770211,"title":"#推薦 運動營養完全指南","content":"http://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZS.jpg\n\n本書是暢銷25年的運動營養聖經，已是第八版。第一次閱讀 The Complete Guide to Sports Nutrition。是95年攻讀MIT時，忘記是二版還三版。\n\n本書適用一般有運動習慣的人。但如果你是運動員與營養師，本書更該讀。比如-平常：關於運動後如何增補最佳蛋白質類型、數量以及時機\n-阻力訓練：理解增補優質蛋白質的時機和如何優化身體組成的方法\n-馬拉松或三鐵：這種高門檻運動，如何防止運動中脫水和確保不會過度補充水分之間找到折衷方案\n\n其實，吃得好對運動者而言，根本事半功倍。很多人可能不知道，甚至靠吃都可以吃出一身肌肉，當然這有些前提，最低量的訓練，中瘦型身材。\n\n非常補的書。","excerpt":"本書是暢銷25年的運動營養聖經，已是第八版。第一次閱讀 The Complete Guide to Sports Nutrition。是95年攻讀MIT時，忘記是二版還三版。本書適用一般有運動習慣的人","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f4388191-41f8-428d-af69-d07d4481dc9e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-27T06:50:25.784Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T07:47:40.211Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["運動","營養","馬拉松","跑步","飲食"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"運動","forumAlias":"sport","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":9},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZS.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"81bb945f-e40e-48f3-ad0d-6f2885129ebf","url":"https://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZSl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZSl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZSl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-27T07:47:40.211Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T07:47:40.211Z"},{"id":"81bb945f-e40e-48f3-ad0d-6f2885129ebf","url":"http://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZS.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/ZU3nDZS","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/ZU3nDZSl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-27T07:47:40.211Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T07:47:40.211Z"}],"postAvatar":""}